loop = OptimizationLoop.with_evaluation_function(parameters=[{'name': 'x1',
    'type': 'range', 'bounds': [-5.0, 10.0], 'value_type': 'float',
    'log_scale': False}, {'name': 'x2', 'type': 'range', 'bounds': [0.0, 
    10.0]}], minimize=True, evaluation_function=
    _branin_evaluation_function_with_unknown_sem, parameter_constraints=[
    'x1 + x2 <= 20'], total_trials=6)
bp, _ = loop.full_run().get_best_point()
self.assertIn('x1', bp)
self.assertIn('x2', bp)
